OL,3,C'Coward' jailed for kicking homeless
OL,4,Cwoman in head in city centre
OL,6,FA man has been jailed after kicking a
OL,7,Fhomeless woman in the head in
OL,8,FWiltshire while she was lying on the
OL,9,Ffloor.
OL,11,FAt around 3am on 17 January 2026,
OL,12,FAaron Nomicas, 20, was walking through
OL,13,FMarket Walk in Salisbury city centre
OL,14,Fwhen he kicked the woman, who was in
OL,15,Fher 50s, as she was lying in the
OL,16,Fwalkway.
OL,18,FNomicas did not know the victim, who
OL,19,Fsuffered facial injuries which are not
OL,20,Fthought to be life-changing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
