PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773155489
OL,3,C'Coward' jailed for kicking homeless
OL,4,Cwoman in head in city centre
OL,6,FNomicas then had to be restrained by
OL,7,Fthe people with him after the victim
OL,8,Fcalled him a coward.
OL,10,FThe incident was reported to police
OL,11,Fthe same day and, following
OL,12,Finvestigations, Nomicas was identified
OL,13,Fand arrested.
OL,15,FNomicas, from Larkhill, was jailed for
OL,16,F6 months on Friday (6 March) at
OL,17,FSalisbury Magistrates' Court after
OL,18,Fpleading guilty to assault occasioning
OL,19,Factual bodily harm.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
