PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773155489
OL,3,C'Coward' jailed for kicking homeless
OL,4,Cwoman in head in city centre
OL,6,FSgt Joshua Bliss said: "This was a
OL,7,Fhighly impactful case ` the victim is
OL,8,Fincredibly vulnerable and had no way
OL,9,Fof protecting herself, or escaping
OL,10,Ffrom, this vicious and unprovoked
OL,11,Fattack.
OL,13,F"She was sat in Salisbury city centre
OL,14,Fwith her dog, Lance, minding her own
OL,15,Fbusiness and simply trying to keep
OL,16,Fwarm.
OL,26,@nD@XOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
