PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1773155489
OL,3,C'Coward' jailed for kicking homeless
OL,4,Cwoman in head in city centre
OL,6,F"The suspect was unknown to the
OL,7,Fvictim, and within only two hours of
OL,8,Fthe investigation commencing, CID
OL,9,Fdetectives and Neighbourhood officers
OL,10,Fidentified and located the offender.
OL,12,F"In the victim's account, she
OL,13,Fdescribes the offender as a 'coward'.
OL,14,FThis is a sentiment shared by those
OL,15,Finvolved in the investigation who saw
OL,16,Fthe CCTV footage showing the attack.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
