OL,3,C'Coward' jailed for kicking homeless
OL,4,Cwoman in head in city centre
OL,6,F"This court result should send a clear
OL,7,Fmessage ` if you are someone who preys
OL,8,Fon the most vulnerable and defenceless
OL,9,Fmembers of our community, we will
OL,10,Fswiftly track you down and we will
OL,11,Fbring you to justice."
